description: Lists all the custom patterns that have been created.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: A list of key-value pair tags. (string) --- (string) ---

nested_items.name: CustomEntityTypes
nested_items.description: A list of CustomEntityType objects representing custom patterns.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A name for the custom pattern that allows it to be retrieved or deleted later. This name must be unique per Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: RegexString
nested_items.description: A regular expression string that is used for detecting sensitive data in a custom pattern.

nested_items.name: ContextWords
nested_items.description: A list of context words. If none of these context words are found within the vicinity of the regular expression the data will not be detected as sensitive data.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token, if more results are available.
